01  WS-DATA-AREA.
    05  WS-NUMBER PIC 9(5) VALUE 0.
    05  WS-FLAG PIC X VALUE 'N'.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    PERFORM 100-INITIALIZE.
    PERFORM 200-PROCESS-DATA UNTIL WS-FLAG = 'Y'.
    DISPLAY "Processing complete."
    STOP RUN.

100-INITIALIZE SECTION.
    MOVE 12345 TO WS-NUMBER.

200-PROCESS-DATA SECTION.
    IF WS-NUMBER > 50000 
        MOVE 'Y' TO WS-FLAG
    ELSE
        ADD 1000 TO WS-NUMBER
        DISPLAY WS-NUMBER
        IF WS-NUMBER > 50000
            MOVE 'Y' TO WS-FLAG
        END-IF
    END-IF.
